hopobject.body: Who's calling? mccracken pharmacy hours For the past seven years, the Jiangshan school has sent groups of pupils in their first year of senior high to experience U.S. summer camps during the Chinese school break. Although no previous major incidents have been reported, one parent wrote last year to the Jiangshan city government questioning safety procedures. The parent also queried who paid for accompanying teachers, and asked for a breakdown of the almost $5,000 fee for a trip of under three weeks.
